headline: Starbucks (SBUX) Valuation Check as Niccol’s Overhaul, Barista Strike and China Push Reshape Investor Expectations
summary: Starbucks (SBUX) is in one of those rare stretches where nearly everything hits at once, with CEO Brian Niccol’s overhaul colliding with a nationwide barista strike and a big strategic push in China. See our latest analysis for Starbucks. Those crosscurrents have left sentiment mixed, with modest recent share price returns despite solid revenue and earnings growth. The 1 year total shareholder return is still in negative territory as investors weigh transformation benefits against labor and...
